OOC: Yeah, I didnt even think about the spinning.

His gas took on the form of the wind current, and began to be pushed away,
almost hitting Cliffjumper, if he wasnt so agile. He looked at the end of
the fight, through his one good eye. He moved towards the downed Halucigen,
and aims his laser pistol at him. "Dont move, or your dust" he threatened.
"What did you do to him" he said, pointing to Prowl.
